---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us" description="Discover the philosophy behind Bali Encore - a boutique travel design house guided by the ancient Balinese wisdom of the Three Cosmos.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center bg-stone-900 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-b from-stone-900/60 via-stone-900/40 to-stone-900/80 z-10"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558005530-a7958896ec60?auto=format&fit=crop&w=2000&q=80')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-20 text-center px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="hero-animate text-gold-500 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6">About Bali Encore</p>
      <h1 class="hero-animate hero-animate-delay-1 font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl text-stone-50 leading-tight">
        The Architecture<br/>of Balance
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Bali Encore -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal">
        <p class="text-gold-600 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6">The Art of the Meaningful Return</p>
        <div class="divider divider-center mb-12"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="prose-luxury reveal text-center">
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif text-stone-800 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          At Bali Encore, we believe in the evolution of business and human consciousness.
        </p>
        <p>
          We are a boutique travel design house based in Ubud, founded on the conviction that 
          travel should be a transformative force—one that elevates the guest while honoring 
          the sanctity of the destination.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our foundation is built upon the ancient Balinese wisdom of the Three Cosmos—Bhur, 
          Bwah, and Swah. We recognize that true luxury is a state of equilibrium.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Three Cosmos Philosophy -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-stone-900 text-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-20 reveal">
        <p class="text-gold-500 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6">Our Philosophy</p>
        <div class="divider divider-center mb-12"></div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-stone-50 mb-8">
          The Three Cosmos
        </h2>
        <p class="text-stone-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Our approach is guided by the ancient Balinese wisdom of balance, known as the 
          Three Cosmos—a harmony between Earth, Humanity, and the Divine.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12 reveal-stagger">
        <!-- Bhur -->
        <div class="text-center border border-stone-800 p-10">
          <div class="inline-block mb-6">
            <span class="font-serif text-5xl text-gold-500">भूर्</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-50 mb-2">Bhur</h3>
          <p class="text-gold-500 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">Nature</p>
          <p class="text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">
            Our commitment to the Earth through sustainable ESG practices and regenerative 
            exploration. The physical connection to the land—walking lightly, supporting 
            local farmers, and protecting the environment.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Bwah -->
        <div class="text-center border border-stone-800 p-10">
          <div class="inline-block mb-6">
            <span class="font-serif text-5xl text-gold-500">भुवः</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-50 mb-2">Bwah</h3>
          <p class="text-gold-500 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">Humanity</p>
          <p class="text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">
            The creation of authentic, personalized connections through culture, luxury 
            hospitality, and adventure. The realm of daily life, rituals, and human 
            interaction—our Boutique Travel Design.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Swah -->
        <div class="text-center border border-stone-800 p-10">
          <div class="inline-block mb-6">
            <span class="font-serif text-5xl text-gold-500">स्वः</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-50 mb-2">Swah</h3>
          <p class="text-gold-500 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">Spirit</p>
          <p class="text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">
            The pursuit of higher consciousness through wellness, healing, and spiritual 
            discovery. The realm of the divine—meditation, sacred water purifications, 
            and the evolution of consciousness.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Do -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal">
        <p class="text-gold-600 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6">What We Do</p>
        <div class="divider divider-center mb-12"></div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-stone-900 mb-8">
          Sustainable Quality Over Mass Tourism
        </h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="prose-luxury reveal">
        <p>
          We move away from mass tourism to focus on Sustainable Quality. As local experts, 
          we design "Organic Structures"—highly personalized itineraries that adapt to the 
          rhythm of our clients.
        </p>
        <p>
          Whether you seek the adrenaline of Adventure, the stillness of Spirituality, or 
          the wisdom of Culture, we curate every detail to ensure your journey is unique, 
          ethical, and deeply authentic.
        </p>
        <p>
          No two travelers are the same—and neither are our journeys. Every itinerary is 
          created exclusively for you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Four Pillars of Identity -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-stone-100">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal">
        <p class="text-gold-600 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6">Our Identity</p>
        <div class="divider divider-center mb-12"></div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-stone-900 mb-8">
          The Four Pillars
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 reveal-stagger">
        <div class="bg-stone-50 p-10 border border-stone-200">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-stone-900 mb-4">A Bespoke Design House</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            We create "Organic Structures" for every journey. No two itineraries are the same. 
            We listen to your intentions and design a narrative that moves at your personal rhythm.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-stone-50 p-10 border border-stone-200">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-stone-900 mb-4">A Bridge to the Three Cosmos</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            Our work is rooted in the Balinese philosophy of balance. We harmonize the Earth 
            (Bhur), the Human (Bwah), and the Spirit (Swah) in every experience we create.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-stone-50 p-10 border border-stone-200">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-stone-900 mb-4">A Leader in Sustainable Luxury</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            We prove that high-end hospitality and ethics can thrive together. Through carbon-offsetting, 
            plastic-free logistics, and direct social investment into local villages, we ensure your 
            presence nourishes the island.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-stone-50 p-10 border border-stone-200">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-stone-900 mb-4">The Local Authority</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            Founded by Bagus Jnana, a son of Bali, we provide a "Master Key" to the island. We move 
            beyond commercial tourism to offer private access to royal palaces, sacred forests, and 
            authentic spiritual initiations.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Founder's Vision -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="relative h-125 reveal-scale image-reveal order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552733407-5d5c46c3bb3b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal order-1 lg:order-2">
          <p class="text-gold-600 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6">The Founder's Dharma</p>
          <div class="divider mb-8"></div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-stone-900 mb-8">
            Our Founder's Vision
          </h2>
          <div class="prose-luxury">
            <p class="text-xl italic text-stone-700 mb-6">
              "As a son of Bali, I created Bali Encore to bridge the gap between world-class 
              luxury and our sacred heritage."
            </p>
            <p>
              We invite the global traveler to return to Bali—not just as a visitor, but as 
              a part of our island's sustainable future.
            </p>
            <p>
              My purpose is to ensure that as Bali evolves, its soul remains intact. I invite 
              the global citizen to experience a Bali that is quality-driven, spiritually 
              aligned, and sustainably managed.
            </p>
            <p class="font-medium text-stone-800">
              — Bagus Jnana, Founder
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- A Message from Bagus Jnana -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-stone-900 text-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="text-gold-500 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6">A Personal Message</p>
        <div class="divider divider-center mb-12"></div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-stone-50 mb-12">
          From Bagus Jnana
        </h2>
        <div class="prose-luxury text-center text-stone-300">
          <p class="text-xl italic mb-8">
            "Growing up in Ubud, I learned that Bali's beauty isn't just in its landscapes, 
            but in the balance we maintain every day."
          </p>
          <p>
            I created Bali Encore because I want to share the 'Real Bali'—the one that exists 
            beyond the camera lens. When you journey with us, you are not just a visitor; 
            you are a guest of my culture.
          </p>
          <p>
            I personally ensure that every ritual we share and every path we walk is done 
            with respect, authenticity, and a commitment to our island's future.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gold-500 font-medium mt-8">
            I look forward to welcoming you home.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="relative py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1501785888041-af3ef285b470?auto=format&fit=crop&w=2000&q=80')] bg-cover bg-center bg-fixed"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-stone-900/70"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center px-6 reveal">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-stone-50 mb-8">
        Ready to Design Your Encore?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-stone-300 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
        Your journey to Bali starts with a conversation. Let us build an organic 
        structure for your next transformation.
      </p>
      <a href="/begin" class="btn-luxury-outline">Inquire with Our Private Concierge</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
